data.description: Begin your journey in this charming one-story 3-bedroom, 2-bath home in San Antonio, Texas 78254. Enjoy an open layout, a well-equipped kitchen, and a spacious master suite with an en suite bathroom  and walk-in closet. The screened-in covered porch adds extra appeal for year-round outdoor enjoyment. Natural light fills the home, creating a warm atmosphere. With a private backyard and a two-car garage, this home is both practical and inviting. Conveniently located near schools, shopping, dining and parks, it offers the ideal blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss out on making this your dream home today!
